item.title: My monkey wife
item.description:
My monkey wife

I had just looked up and couldn’t complete the sentence. Bert stood before me. I mean I thought it was Bert. He had the same voice, was wearing the same uniform that I am sure he never washed and he had this stupid grin on his stupid face. Except it wasn’t his face. It was the face of … of …. “You’re an Ape.” I heard myself say.
